80static const struct cv {
81 uint64_t clsid[2];
82 const char *mime;
83} clsid2mime[] = {
84 {
85 { 0x00000000000c1084ULL, 0x46000000000000c0ULL },
86 "x-msi",
87 },
88 { { 0, 0 },
89 NULL,
90 },
91}, clsid2desc[] = {
92 {
93 { 0x00000000000c1084ULL, 0x46000000000000c0ULL },
94 "MSI Installer",
95 },
96 { { 0, 0 },
97 NULL,
98 },
99};

101private const char *
102cdf_clsid_to_mime(const uint64_t clsid[2], const struct cv *cv)
103{
104 size_t i;
105 for (i = 0; cv[i].mime != NULL; i++) {
106 if (clsid[0] == cv[i].clsid[0] && clsid[1] == cv[i].clsid[1])
107 return cv[i].mime;
108 }
109#ifdef CDF_DEBUG
110 fprintf(stderr, "unknown mime %" PRIx64 ", %" PRIx64 "\n", clsid[0],
111 clsid[1]);
112#endif
113 return NULL;
114}
115
116private const char *
117cdf_app_to_mime(const char *vbuf, const struct nv *nv)
118{
119 size_t i;
120 const char *rv = NULL;
121#ifdef USE_C_LOCALE
122 locale_t old_lc_ctype, c_lc_ctype;
123
124 c_lc_ctype = newlocale(LC_CTYPE_MASK, "C", 0);
125 assert(c_lc_ctype != NULL);
126 old_lc_ctype = uselocale(c_lc_ctype);
127 assert(old_lc_ctype != NULL);
128#else
129 char *old_lc_ctype = setlocale(LC_CTYPE, "C");
130#endif
131 for (i = 0; nv[i].pattern != NULL; i++)
132 if (strcasestr(vbuf, nv[i].pattern) != NULL) {
133 rv = nv[i].mime;
134 break;
135 }
136#ifdef CDF_DEBUG
137 fprintf(stderr, "unknown app %s\n", vbuf);
138#endif
139#ifdef USE_C_LOCALE
140 (void)uselocale(old_lc_ctype);
141 freelocale(c_lc_ctype);
142#else
143 setlocale(LC_CTYPE, old_lc_ctype);
144#endif
145 return rv;
146}

148private int
149cdf_file_property_info(struct magic_set *ms, const cdf_property_info_t *info,
150 size_t count, const cdf_directory_t *root_storage)
151{
152 size_t i;
153 cdf_timestamp_t tp;
154 struct timespec ts;
155 char buf[64];
156 const char *str = NULL;
157 const char *s, *e;
158 int len;
159
160 if (!NOTMIME(ms) && root_storage)
161 str = cdf_clsid_to_mime(root_storage->d_storage_uuid,
162 clsid2mime);
163
164 for (i = 0; i < count; i++) {
165 cdf_print_property_name(buf, sizeof(buf), info[i].pi_id);
166 switch (info[i].pi_type) {
167 case CDF_NULL:
168 break;
169 case CDF_SIGNED16:
170 if (NOTMIME(ms) && file_printf(ms, ", %s: %hd", buf,
171 info[i].pi_s16) == -1)
172 return -1;
173 break;
174 case CDF_SIGNED32:
175 if (NOTMIME(ms) && file_printf(ms, ", %s: %d", buf,
176 info[i].pi_s32) == -1)
177 return -1;
178 break;
179 case CDF_UNSIGNED32:
180 if (NOTMIME(ms) && file_printf(ms, ", %s: %u", buf,
181 info[i].pi_u32) == -1)
182 return -1;
183 break;
184 case CDF_FLOAT:
185 if (NOTMIME(ms) && file_printf(ms, ", %s: %g", buf,
186 info[i].pi_f) == -1)
187 return -1;
188 break;
189 case CDF_DOUBLE:
190 if (NOTMIME(ms) && file_printf(ms, ", %s: %g", buf,
191 info[i].pi_d) == -1)
192 return -1;
193 break;
194 case CDF_LENGTH32_STRING:
195 case CDF_LENGTH32_WSTRING:
196 len = info[i].pi_str.s_len;
197 if (len > 1) {
198 char vbuf[1024];
199 size_t j, k = 1;
200
201 if (info[i].pi_type == CDF_LENGTH32_WSTRING)
202 k++;
203 s = info[i].pi_str.s_buf;
204 e = info[i].pi_str.s_buf + len;
205 for (j = 0; s < e && j < sizeof(vbuf)
206 && len--; s += k) {
207 if (*s == '\0')
208 break;
209 if (isprint(CAST(unsigned char, *s)))
210 vbuf[j++] = *s;
211 }
212 if (j == sizeof(vbuf))
213 --j;
214 vbuf[j] = '\0';
215 if (NOTMIME(ms)) {
216 if (vbuf[0]) {
217 if (file_printf(ms, ", %s: %s",
218 buf, vbuf) == -1)
219 return -1;
220 }
221 } else if (str == NULL && info[i].pi_id ==
222 CDF_PROPERTY_NAME_OF_APPLICATION) {
223 str = cdf_app_to_mime(vbuf, app2mime);
224 }
225 }
226 break;
227 case CDF_FILETIME:
228 tp = info[i].pi_tp;
229 if (tp != 0) {
230 char tbuf[64];
231 if (tp < 1000000000000000LL) {
232 cdf_print_elapsed_time(tbuf,
233 sizeof(tbuf), tp);
234 if (NOTMIME(ms) && file_printf(ms,
235 ", %s: %s", buf, tbuf) == -1)
236 return -1;
237 } else {
238 char *c, *ec;
239 cdf_timestamp_to_timespec(&ts, tp);
240 c = cdf_ctime(&ts.tv_sec, tbuf);
241 if (c != NULL &&
242 (ec = strchr(c, '\n')) != NULL)
243 *ec = '\0';
244
245 if (NOTMIME(ms) && file_printf(ms,
246 ", %s: %s", buf, c) == -1)
247 return -1;
248 }
249 }
250 break;
251 case CDF_CLIPBOARD:
252 break;
253 default:
254 return -1;
255 }
256 }
257 if (ms->flags & MAGIC_MIME_TYPE) {
258 if (str == NULL)
259 return 0;
260 if (file_printf(ms, "application/%s", str) == -1)
261 return -1;
262 }
263 return 1;
264}

266private int
267cdf_file_catalog(struct magic_set *ms, const cdf_header_t *h,
268 const cdf_stream_t *sst)
269{
270 cdf_catalog_t *cat;
271 size_t i;
272 char buf[256];
273 cdf_catalog_entry_t *ce;
274
275 if (NOTMIME(ms)) {
276 if (file_printf(ms, "Microsoft Thumbs.db [") == -1)
277 return -1;
278 if (cdf_unpack_catalog(h, sst, &cat) == -1)
279 return -1;
280 ce = cat->cat_e;
281 /* skip first entry since it has a , or paren */
282 for (i = 1; i < cat->cat_num; i++)
283 if (file_printf(ms, "%s%s",
284 cdf_u16tos8(buf, ce[i].ce_namlen, ce[i].ce_name),
285 i == cat->cat_num - 1 ? "]" : ", ") == -1) {
286 free(cat);
287 return -1;
288 }
289 free(cat);
290 } else if (ms->flags & MAGIC_MIME_TYPE) {
291 if (file_printf(ms, "application/CDFV2") == -1)
292 return -1;
293 }
294 return 1;
295}
296
297private int
298cdf_file_summary_info(struct magic_set *ms, const cdf_header_t *h,
299 const cdf_stream_t *sst, const cdf_directory_t *root_storage)
300{
301 cdf_summary_info_header_t si;
302 cdf_property_info_t *info;
303 size_t count;
304 int m;
305
306 if (cdf_unpack_summary_info(sst, h, &si, &info, &count) == -1)
307 return -1;
308
309 if (NOTMIME(ms)) {
310 const char *str;
311
312 if (file_printf(ms, "Composite Document File V2 Document")
313 == -1)
314 return -1;
315
316 if (file_printf(ms, ", %s Endian",
317 si.si_byte_order == 0xfffe ? "Little" : "Big") == -1)
318 return -2;
319 switch (si.si_os) {
320 case 2:
321 if (file_printf(ms, ", Os: Windows, Version %d.%d",
322 si.si_os_version & 0xff,
323 CAST(uint32_t, si.si_os_version) >> 8) == -1)
324 return -2;
325 break;
326 case 1:
327 if (file_printf(ms, ", Os: MacOS, Version %d.%d",
328 CAST(uint32_t, si.si_os_version) >> 8,
329 si.si_os_version & 0xff) == -1)
330 return -2;
331 break;
332 default:
333 if (file_printf(ms, ", Os %d, Version: %d.%d", si.si_os,
334 si.si_os_version & 0xff,
335 CAST(uint32_t, si.si_os_version) >> 8) == -1)
336 return -2;
337 break;
338 }
339 if (root_storage) {
340 str = cdf_clsid_to_mime(root_storage->d_storage_uuid,
341 clsid2desc);
342 if (str) {
343 if (file_printf(ms, ", %s", str) == -1)
344 return -2;
345 }
346 }
347 }
348
349 m = cdf_file_property_info(ms, info, count, root_storage);
350 free(info);
351
352 return m == -1 ? -2 : m;
353}
354
355#ifdef notdef
356private char *
357format_clsid(char *buf, size_t len, const uint64_t uuid[2]) {
358 snprintf(buf, len, "%.8" PRIx64 "-%.4" PRIx64 "-%.4" PRIx64 "-%.4"
359 PRIx64 "-%.12" PRIx64,
360 (uuid[0] >> 32) & (uint64_t)0x000000000ffffffffULL,
361 (uuid[0] >> 16) & (uint64_t)0x0000000000000ffffULL,
362 (uuid[0] >> 0) & (uint64_t)0x0000000000000ffffULL,
363 (uuid[1] >> 48) & (uint64_t)0x0000000000000ffffULL,
364 (uuid[1] >> 0) & (uint64_t)0x0000fffffffffffffULL);
365 return buf;
366}
367#endif

369private int
370cdf_file_catalog_info(struct magic_set *ms, const cdf_info_t *info,
371 const cdf_header_t *h, const cdf_sat_t *sat, const cdf_sat_t *ssat,
372 const cdf_stream_t *sst, const cdf_dir_t *dir, cdf_stream_t *scn)
373{
374 int i;
375
376 if ((i = cdf_read_user_stream(info, h, sat, ssat, sst,
377 dir, "Catalog", scn)) == -1)
378 return i;
379#ifdef CDF_DEBUG
380 cdf_dump_catalog(h, scn);
381#endif
382 if ((i = cdf_file_catalog(ms, h, scn)) == -1)
383 return -1;
384 return i;
385}
386
387private int
388cdf_check_summary_info(struct magic_set *ms, const cdf_info_t *info,
389 const cdf_header_t *h, const cdf_sat_t *sat, const cdf_sat_t *ssat,
390 const cdf_stream_t *sst, const cdf_dir_t *dir, cdf_stream_t *scn,
391 const cdf_directory_t *root_storage, const char **expn)
392{
393 int i;
394 const char *str = NULL;
395 cdf_directory_t *d;
396 char name[__arraycount(d->d_name)];
397 size_t j, k;
398
399#ifdef CDF_DEBUG
400 cdf_dump_summary_info(h, scn);
401#endif
402 if ((i = cdf_file_summary_info(ms, h, scn, root_storage)) < 0) {
403 *expn = "Can't expand summary_info";
404 return i;
405 }
406 if (i == 1)
407 return i;
408 for (j = 0; str == NULL && j < dir->dir_len; j++) {
409 d = &dir->dir_tab[j];
410 for (k = 0; k < sizeof(name); k++)
411 name[k] = CAST(char, cdf_tole2(d->d_name[k]));
412 str = cdf_app_to_mime(name,
413 NOTMIME(ms) ? name2desc : name2mime);
414 }
415 if (NOTMIME(ms)) {
416 if (str != NULL) {
417 if (file_printf(ms, "%s", str) == -1)
418 return -1;
419 i = 1;
420 }
421 } else if (ms->flags & MAGIC_MIME_TYPE) {
422 if (str == NULL)
423 str = "vnd.ms-office";
424 if (file_printf(ms, "application/%s", str) == -1)
425 return -1;
426 i = 1;
427 }
428 if (i <= 0) {
429 i = cdf_file_catalog_info(ms, info, h, sat, ssat, sst,
430 dir, scn);
431 }
432 return i;
433}

512private int
513cdf_file_dir_info(struct magic_set *ms, const cdf_dir_t *dir)
514{
515 size_t sd, j;
516
517 for (sd = 0; sd < __arraycount(sectioninfo); sd++) {
518 const struct sinfo *si = &sectioninfo[sd];
519 for (j = 0; si->sections[j]; j++) {
520 if (cdf_find_stream(dir, si->sections[j], si->types[j])
521 > 0)
522 break;
523#ifdef CDF_DEBUG
524 fprintf(stderr, "Can't read %s\n", si->sections[j]);
525#endif
526 }
527 if (si->sections[j] == NULL)
528 continue;
529 if (NOTMIME(ms)) {
530 if (file_printf(ms, "CDFV2 %s", si->name) == -1)
531 return -1;
532 } else if (ms->flags & MAGIC_MIME_TYPE) {
533 if (file_printf(ms, "application/%s", si->mime) == -1)
534 return -1;
535 }
536 return 1;
537 }
538 return -1;
539}
540
541protected int
542file_trycdf(struct magic_set *ms, const struct buffer *b)
543{
544 int fd = b->fd;
545 const unsigned char *buf = CAST(const unsigned char *, b->fbuf);
546 size_t nbytes = b->flen;
547 cdf_info_t info;
548 cdf_header_t h;
549 cdf_sat_t sat, ssat;
550 cdf_stream_t sst, scn;
551 cdf_dir_t dir;
552 int i;
553 const char *expn = "";
554 const cdf_directory_t *root_storage;
555
556 scn.sst_tab = NULL;
557 info.i_fd = fd;
558 info.i_buf = buf;
559 info.i_len = nbytes;
560 if (ms->flags & (MAGIC_APPLE|MAGIC_EXTENSION))
561 return 0;
562 if (cdf_read_header(&info, &h) == -1)
563 return 0;
564#ifdef CDF_DEBUG
565 cdf_dump_header(&h);
566#endif
567
568 if ((i = cdf_read_sat(&info, &h, &sat)) == -1) {
569 expn = "Can't read SAT";
570 goto out0;
571 }
572#ifdef CDF_DEBUG
573 cdf_dump_sat("SAT", &sat, CDF_SEC_SIZE(&h));
574#endif
575
576 if ((i = cdf_read_ssat(&info, &h, &sat, &ssat)) == -1) {
577 expn = "Can't read SSAT";
578 goto out1;
579 }
580#ifdef CDF_DEBUG
581 cdf_dump_sat("SSAT", &ssat, CDF_SHORT_SEC_SIZE(&h));
582#endif
583
584 if ((i = cdf_read_dir(&info, &h, &sat, &dir)) == -1) {
585 expn = "Can't read directory";
586 goto out2;
587 }
588
589 if ((i = cdf_read_short_stream(&info, &h, &sat, &dir, &sst,
590 &root_storage)) == -1) {
591 expn = "Cannot read short stream";
592 goto out3;
593 }
594#ifdef CDF_DEBUG
595 cdf_dump_dir(&info, &h, &sat, &ssat, &sst, &dir);
596#endif
597#ifdef notdef
598 if (root_storage) {
599 if (NOTMIME(ms)) {
600 char clsbuf[128];
601 if (file_printf(ms, "CLSID %s, ",
602 format_clsid(clsbuf, sizeof(clsbuf),
603 root_storage->d_storage_uuid)) == -1)
604 return -1;
605 }
606 }
607#endif
608
609 if ((i = cdf_read_user_stream(&info, &h, &sat, &ssat, &sst, &dir,
610 "FileHeader", &scn)) != -1) {
611#define HWP5_SIGNATURE "HWP Document File"
612 if (scn.sst_len * scn.sst_ss >= sizeof(HWP5_SIGNATURE) - 1
613 && memcmp(scn.sst_tab, HWP5_SIGNATURE,
614 sizeof(HWP5_SIGNATURE) - 1) == 0) {
615 if (NOTMIME(ms)) {
616 if (file_printf(ms,
617 "Hangul (Korean) Word Processor File 5.x") == -1)
618 return -1;
619 } else if (ms->flags & MAGIC_MIME_TYPE) {
620 if (file_printf(ms, "application/x-hwp") == -1)
621 return -1;
622 }
623 i = 1;
624 goto out5;
625 } else {
626 cdf_zero_stream(&scn);
627 }
628 }
629
630 if ((i = cdf_read_summary_info(&info, &h, &sat, &ssat, &sst, &dir,
631 &scn)) == -1) {
632 if (errno != ESRCH) {
633 expn = "Cannot read summary info";
634 }
635 } else {
636 i = cdf_check_summary_info(ms, &info, &h,
637 &sat, &ssat, &sst, &dir, &scn, root_storage, &expn);
638 cdf_zero_stream(&scn);
639 }
640 if (i <= 0) {
641 if ((i = cdf_read_doc_summary_info(&info, &h, &sat, &ssat,
642 &sst, &dir, &scn)) == -1) {
643 if (errno != ESRCH) {
644 expn = "Cannot read summary info";
645 }
646 } else {
647 i = cdf_check_summary_info(ms, &info, &h, &sat, &ssat,
648 &sst, &dir, &scn, root_storage, &expn);
649 }
650 }
651 if (i <= 0) {
652 i = cdf_file_dir_info(ms, &dir);
653 if (i < 0)
654 expn = "Cannot read section info";
655 }
656out5:
657 cdf_zero_stream(&scn);
658 cdf_zero_stream(&sst);
659out3:
660 free(dir.dir_tab);
661out2:
662 free(ssat.sat_tab);
663out1:
664 free(sat.sat_tab);
665out0:
666 /* If we handled it already, return */
667 if (i != -1)
668 return i;
669 /* Provide a default handler */
670 if (NOTMIME(ms)) {
671 if (file_printf(ms,
672 "Composite Document File V2 Document") == -1)
673 return -1;
674 if (*expn)
675 if (file_printf(ms, ", %s", expn) == -1)
676 return -1;
677 } else if (ms->flags & MAGIC_MIME_TYPE) {
678 if (file_printf(ms, "application/CDFV2") == -1)
679 return -1;
680 }
681 return 1;
682}
